'''Yù-thai-kau''' he chhai kûng-ngièn chhièn lióng-chhiên-ngièn [[Chûng-tûng]] thi-khî ke yù-mu̍k mìn-chhu̍k [[Hî-pak-lòi-ngìn]] chûng sán-sên ke.

Yù-thai-kau chhùng-pai tân-yit ke chú-sṳ̀n Adonai, he Hî-pak-lòi-ngìn nui-phu ke mìn-chhu̍k [[Chûng-kau]]. Yù-thai-kau ngin-vì "Thap-muk-tet" he [[Sṳn-kîn]] ke kîn-si̍t, chhiùng Yù-thai-kau chûng-phai sâng-chhut lióng-ke sṳ-kie chui-thai ke chûng-kau—— [[Kî-tuk-kau]] lâu [[Yî-sṳ̂-làn-kau]]. Tông-sṳ̀ [[Â-li̍t-sân-thai thai-ti]] chṳ̂n-fu̍k Hî-pak-lòi-ngìn ke Yù-thai-thi heu, Hî-pak-lòi-ngìn ya yi-miàng vi [[Yù-thai-ngìn]] pin san-lo̍k to [[Hî-lia̍p-ti-koet]] kok-chhu.

